title: [Morgause's Outfitting]
[Morgause's General Store]
[Morgause's Magic Shoppe]
description: Beneath a swirl-painted white stucco ceiling, a tattered merchant permit hangs on one of the knotty oak-paneled walls.  A heavy white granite counter and a white marble shelf sit in opposite corners while a worn rug rests on a black-checked white tile floor.
